<div id="key-bindings" class="fixed bottom-10 right-4 bg-gray-800 border border-green-400 p-4 rounded hidden">
  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Key Bindings</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><kbd>j</kbd> / <kbd>k</kbd>: Navigate up/down</li>
    <li><kbd>u</kbd>: Go back</li>
    <li><kbd>g</kbd>: Go to top</li>
    <li><kbd>G</kbd>: Go to bottom</li>
    <li><kbd>/</kbd>: Focus search</li>
    <li><kbd>:</kbd><span class="text-blue">&lt;command&gt;</span> : Navigate to <span class="text-blue">&lt;command&gt;</span></li>
    <li><kbd>Esc</kbd>: Clear search / Exit</li>
  </ul>
</div>
